cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is primarily focused on video anomaly detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a self-trained deep ordinal regression approach, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on real-world video scenes, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and computer security (cs.CR) categories.
